<br>
Now be sure to add some serious UNBUFFED resists to that.  If you are 47 you need some serious resists.  I've been on raids and talked to people going on raids that have NO RESIST gear.  Many being shaman/druids that say &quot;Oh well I can buff my resists&quot;.  Sorry that don't cut it.  Dragons dispell your buffs.  <br>
<br>
I would recommend having at least 100 MR and 100 FR/CR (depending on which dragon) UNBUFFED.   Luckily for a shaman its much easier getting resist gear than it is for a druid.  Not much out there for druids without spending some serious cash.<br>
<br>
I've been making some lists of resist gears that aren't too hard to get for friends.  Its by no means an expert's list but will give you a good idea of whats out there.<br>
